HCA Said to Price 126.2 Million Shares at $30 Each in Hospital Chain's IPO

-- B y   L e e   S p e a r s
-- 
2011-03-09T22:09:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-09/hca-said-to-price-126-2-million-shares-at-30-each-in-hospital-chain-s-ipo.html
HCA Holdings Inc., the Nashville,
Tennessee-based hospital chain, priced 126.2 million shares at
$30 each in its initial public offering, raising $3.79 billion,
according to two people with knowledge of the matter.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lee Spears in  New York  at 
 lspears3@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:  Jennifer Sondag  at   jsondag@bloomberg.net . 